            <div class="comment_body">
                                                                                                                
                Some folks use mustard, and I've seen some of the cooks on the circuit using squeeze bottle margarine. The idea of using oil is because many of the flavors in the rub are oil soluble, not water soluble, and this helps them flavor the meat.            </div>
            
